    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>In nomine Domini Dei Salvatoris nostri Iesu Christi. Concessemus nos <rs
                            key="#Vir_gloriosus/vir_sublimis">vir gloriosissimus</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/186" key="#Princeps">Sichardus</persName> Dei
                        previdentia Beneventane provincie <rs key="#Princeps">princeps</rs>, <rs
                            key="#Intercessory">per rogum</rs>
                        <persName key="#Other_palatine_officer" ref="#people/3635"
                            >Radelgis</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">thesaurarii</rs> nostri, tibi <persName
                            ref="#people/3634" key="#Other_palatine_officer">Ationi</persName>
                        <rs key="#Other_palatine_officer">gasindio</rs> nostro filio <name ref="Azo"
                            >Ationi</name>
                        <rs
                            key="#Landed_possessions #Fiscal_property #Object #Redistributive #Outflow #Iure_proprietatis/pleno_iure #Allocation_to_individuals"
                            >terram</rs> vacuam in <placeName ref="#places/3437"
                            key="#Villages/settlements #Fiscal_property">Furcle</placeName>
                        <rs key="#Size">modios quindecim</rs> que fuit sacri nostri palatii et
                        pertinet de ipsae <geogName ref="#estates/3425" key="#Curtes"><rs
                                key="#Curtes">curte</rs> Furculana</geogName>, que habet has <rs
                            key="#Fines">fines</rs>: de uno latere et uno capite fine terra tua et
                        Piconis per exiente in viam puplicam; de alio latere finem terra que fuit
                        Leonis et pertinuit de <rs key="#Iudiciaria">iudiciaria</rs>
                        <persName ref="#people/3632" key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">Petri</persName>
                        <rs key="#Gastaldus/vicegastaldus">gastaldei</rs> nostri; in ea videlicet
                        ratione ut amodo et deinceps per hoc nostrum roboreum preceptum predictam
                        terram ut superius legitur tu et heredes tui habere et possidere valeatis,
                        et a nullis ex nostris iudicibus, id est comitibus, gastaldeis vel a
                        quibuscumque agentibus habeatis aliquam requisitionem, sed perpetuis
                        temporibus ipsam terram possideatis. Quod vero preceptum concessionis ex
                        iussione nominate potestatis scripsi ego <persName ref="#people/3460"
                            key="#Notary">Leo</persName>
                        <rs key="#Notary">notarius</rs>. Actum <placeName key="#Cities"
                            ref="#places/110">Beneventi</placeName> in <rs key="#Palatium">in sacro
                            palatio</rs> primo anno, mense octubrio, undecima indictio.
                        Feliciter.</ab>
                </div>
            </div>
